OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA good deal of cloud with some
OL,6,Fsunshine, this hazy at times,
OL,7,Fespecially in the west. Windy in
OL,8,Fplaces with strengthening easterly
OL,9,Fwinds particularly across the moors of
OL,10,FDevon and Cornwall. Feeling pleasant
OL,11,Fout of the wind.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry overnight with variable
OL,14,Famounts of cloud, strong and gusty
OL,15,Fwinds persisting particularly across
OL,16,Fthe west. Chilly with a touch of frost
OL,17,Fpossible in some sheltered spots in
OL,18,Feastern counties.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
