OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FStrong easterly winds on
OL,6,FWednesday with gales possible on
OL,7,Fexposed coasts. An increasing risk of
OL,8,Fshowers in the far west, but always
OL,9,Fsunnier across eastern counties.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,12,FThursday and Friday with high pressure
OL,13,Fdominating. Often sunny and feeling
OL,14,Fwarm by day. Chilly nights as winds
OL,15,Fslowly ease. Cloudier on Saturday with
OL,16,Fa chance of rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
